channel.description: how do I get my 562 up online (or even my 317) and where can I advertise it so that people will log in (and donate :) im using a runeslay source and client and runewings for my 317 so i registered a new server with runelocus and it says online 100% HurrAYYYYY then 45-2 hours later it says offline I didnt change anything and it never goes back online this has happened with three different servers im 90% sure im doing everything right ive portforwarded I have no-ip and its working (i think...) and my server works No one can seem to figure out the problem and if anyone could at least point me in the right direction it would be sooooooooo awesome thanks in advance
